          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1595949264996-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1595949264996-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables are roasted and tender, add the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> to the tray and cook for a further 2-5 min or until toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1595949280259-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
